CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 24, 1959, pg. 22 reads: "Cage Scramble - Roger Parrish, Westinghouse High School guard, battles for a rebound in a City League game against South High on the latter's court last Friday. Other Westinghouse players in picture are Anthony Liscio (35) and Andrien Page.  The Bulldogs won. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Westinghouse basketball players Rodger Parrish #34, Anthony Liscio #35, and Andrien Page, playing against South High School basketball team in a City League game, Westinghouse gymnasium
